items.title: Spotify says Wrapped 2025 is its biggest yet, with 200M+ users in its first day
items.description: After last year's flop, Spotify Wrapped engagement is up 19% and shares were up 41%, the company says.

items.title: Anthropic signs $200M deal to bring its LLMs to Snowflake’s customers
items.description: AI research lab Anthropic inked a $200 million deal with Snowflake to bring its AI models to Snowflake's 12,600 customers.

items.title: AI finds its way into Apple’s top apps of the year

items.title: Nexus isn’t going all-in on AI, keeping half of its new $700M fund for India startups
items.description: Nexus Venture Partners manages $3.2 billion in capital across its funds and has invested in more than 130 companies over the years.
